###Block: Uncanny Dodge and Improved Uncanny Dodge --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Use: ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Uncanny Dodge ~ Base to add the Uncanny Dodge/Improved Uncanny Dodge feature
